sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Posts a journal entry to a GL account in SAP ECC – RFC.

Inputs :

  • Connection Alias - Connection alias for SAP ECC - RFC.
  • Document Header - Complex object containing these fields:
    • Reference procedure
    • Object key
    • Log system source
    • Business Transaction
    • User Name
    • Document Header Text
    • Company Code
    • Document Date
    • Posting Date
    • Fiscal Year
    • Posting period
    • Document type
  • G/L Accounts - Objects containing these fields:
    • Position
    • G/L Account
    • Text
    • Statistical
    • Logical Transaction
    • Document Number
    • Reference Key 1
    • Reference Key 2
    • Reference Key 3
    • Transaction
    • Account type
    • Document type
    • Company Code
    • Business Area
    • Functional Area
    • Plant
    • Posting period
    • Fiscal Year
    • Posting Date
    • Value date
    • FM Area
    • Customer
    • W/o Cash Dscnt
    • Vendor
    • Assignment
    • Tax Code
    • Tax Jurisdiction
    • External object
    • Business Scenario
    • Cost Object
    • Cost Center
    • Activity Type
    • Profit Center
    • Partner Profit Ctr
    • Network
    • WBS element
    • Order
    • Order item number
    • Opertn task list no
    • Activity
    • Condition Type
    • Numerator
    • Level Number
    • Fund
    • Funds center
    • Commitment item
    • Business Process
    • Asset
    • Sub-number
    • Billing Type
    • Sales Order
    • Sales order item
    • Distribution Channel
    • Division
    • Sales Organization
    • Sales Group
    • Sales Office
    • Sold-To Party
    • Subseq debit/credit
    • Elimination PrCtr
    • Quantity updating
    • Quantity
    • Base Unit of Measure
    • Base Unit ISO code
    • Invoiced Quantity
    • Billing qty in SKU
    • Sales Unit
    • Sales unit in ISO
    • Qty in OPUn
    • Order price unit
    • Pur Ord PU ISO
    • Qty in unit of entry
    • Unit of Entry
    • Unit of entry ISO
    • Volume
    • Volume unit
    • Volume unit ISO
    • Gross Weight
    • Net weight
    • Weight unit
    • Unit of weight ISO
    • Item Category
    • Material
    • Material Type
    • Movement indicator
    • Revaluation
    • Origin group
    • Material origin
    • Serial no acct asset
    • Partner
    • Trading part BA
    • Trading Partner
    • Valuation Area
    • Valuation Type
    • Reference date
    • Purchasing Document
    • Item
    • Item (SD)
    • Condition Category
    • Functional Area
    • Commitment item
    • Grant
    • Transaction type
    • Funded Program
    • Segment
    • Partner Segment
    • Earmarked Funds
    • Document Item
    • Billing Period of Performance Start Date
    • Billing Period of Performance End Date
    • PPA Exclude Ind
    • Fast Pay Indicator
    • Partner Grant
    • Budget Period
    • Par Budget Per
    • Partner Fund
    • Document item number for tax document
    • Payment Type
    • Expense Type
    • Program Profile
    • Material
  • Currency Items - Objects containing these fields:
    • Position
    • Crcy type/val view
    • Currency
    • ISO code currency
    • Amount
    • Exchange rate
    • Indirect quoted exchange rate
    • Tax Base Amount
    • Discount Base
    • Discount amount
    • Tax Amount
  • Additional Fields - Additional fields or values you want to add to the details. These fields are retrieved dynamically from SAP ECC - RFC.

Outputs :

  • Journal Entry Data - Journal entry document details.
  • Status - If the request is executed successfully, Status is set to “Success”. If there is a failure in SAP ECC - RFC, Status is set to “Error”.
  • Error Message - Reason for error as returned from SAP ECC - RFC in the RETURN object. Populated only when an error occurs.

Error Messages :

  • Encountered an error. Check log for more details.

To use this action, the corresponding SAP ECC - RFC connection and credential must be created and associated with the SAP_ECC Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.

sys_hub_action_type_snapshot.description:
Posts a journal entry to a GL account in SAP ECC – RFC.

Inputs :

  • Connection Alias - Connection alias for SAP ECC - RFC.
  • Document Header - Complex object containing these fields:
    • Reference procedure
    • Object key
    • Log system source
    • Business Transaction
    • User Name
    • Document Header Text
    • Company Code
    • Document Date
    • Posting Date
    • Fiscal Year
    • Posting period
    • Document type
  • G/L Accounts - Objects containing these fields:
    • Position
    • G/L Account
    • Text
    • Statistical
    • Logical Transaction
    • Document Number
    • Reference Key 1
    • Reference Key 2
    • Reference Key 3
    • Transaction
    • Account type
    • Document type
    • Company Code
    • Business Area

    • Plant
    • Posting period
    • Fiscal Year
    • Posting Date
    • Value date
    • FM Area

    • Asset
    • Sub-number
    • Billing Type
    • Sales Order
    • Sales order item
    • Distribution Channel

    • Sales Group
    • Sales Office
    • Sold-To Party
    • Subseq debit/credit
    • Elimination PrCtr
    • Quantity updating
    • Quantity
    • Base Unit of Measure
    • Base Unit ISO code
    • Invoiced Quantity
    • Billing qty in SKU
    • Sales Unit
    • Sales unit in ISO
    • Qty in OPUn
    • Order price unit
    • Pur Ord PU ISO
    • Qty in unit of entry
    • Unit of Entry
    • Unit of entry ISO
    • Volume
    • Volume unit
    • Volume unit ISO
    • Gross Weight
    • Net weight
    • Weight unit
    • Unit of weight ISO
    • Item Category

    • Movement indicator
    • Revaluation
    • Origin group
    • Material origin
    • Serial no acct asset
    • Partner
    • Trading part BA
    • Trading Partner
    • Valuation Area
    • Valuation Type
    • Reference date
    • Purchasing Document
    • Item
    • Item (SD)
    • Condition Category
    • Functional Area
    • Commitment item
    • Grant
    • Transaction type
    • Funded Program
    • Segment
    • Partner Segment
    • Earmarked Funds
    • Document Item
    • Billing Period of Performance Start Date
    • Billing Period of Performance End Date
    • PPA Exclude Ind
    • Fast Pay Indicator
    • Partner Grant
    • Budget Period
    • Par Budget Per
    • Partner Fund
    • Document item number for tax document
    • Payment Type
    • Expense Type
    • Program Profile
    • Material
  • Currency Items - Objects containing these fields:
    • Position
    • Crcy type/val view
    • Currency
    • ISO code currency
    • Amount
    • Exchange rate
    • Indirect quoted exchange rate
    • Tax Base Amount
    • Discount Base
    • Discount amount
    • Tax Amount
  • Additional Fields - Additional fields or values you want to add to the details. These fields are retrieved dynamically from SAP ECC - RFC.

Outputs :

  • Journal Entry Data - Journal entry document details.
  • Status - If the request is executed successfully, Status is set to “Success”. If there is a failure in SAP ECC - RFC, Status is set to “Error”.
  • Error Message - Reason for error as returned from SAP ECC - RFC in the RETURN object. Populated only when an error occurs.

Error Messages :

  • Encountered an error. Check log for more details.

To use this action, the corresponding SAP ECC - RFC connection and credential must be created and associated with the SAP_ECC Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
